# Type Definitions Rules

## Description
Rules for defining and using types within the MockServer Node project.

## Files
src/types/*.js

## Rules
- Use JSDoc for type annotations
- Export all type definitions for reuse
- Be explicit about object properties and their types
- Prefer simple, flat type structures over deeply nested ones
- Document all types with description comments
- Use consistent naming conventions for types
- Add examples of usage where appropriate
- Keep type definitions separate from business logic
- Update type definitions when related functionality changes 